---
title: "US57 — Review expert applications"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertsApprovalScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ReviewExpertVerification
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertProfile · ExpertVerificationDocument
  A->>B: open pending application + documents
  B->>C: loadApplication(applicationId)
  C->>E: fetchExpertVerification(applicationId)
  E-->>C: ExpertProfile + ExpertVerificationDocument
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (application)
  alt approve
    A->>B: tap APPROVE
    B->>C: decide(applicationId, "verified")
    C->>E: updateExpertVerification(applicationId, "verified")
    E-->>C: ExpertProfile (status = verified)
    B-->>A: expert goes live
  else reject
    A->>B: tap REJECT (+ reason)
    B->>C: decide(applicationId, "rejected")
    C->>E: updateExpertVerification(applicationId, "rejected")
    E-->>C: ExpertProfile (status = rejected)
    B-->>A: applicant notified
  end
  note over E: fetchExpertVerification / updateExpertVerification via SupabaseGateway (RLS admin-only)
